AdvertisementBy JEANNETTE CATSOULISA deeply cynical movie masquerading as a complex moral dilemma, the Australian drama Centering on three detectives, each at different stages of life and career, the story opens on a drug raid as Malcolm (Encasing low-rent ideas with a buffed veneer of sophistication, Even more repellent is Jim, the supposedly straight-arrow novice who sexually exploits the vulnerability of the comatose boy’s mother. “Who is right and who is wrong?” the publicity notes wonder, as if any decent person would ever have the slightest doubt.




